    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im in rio and i think i went too hard in the sun today. my head is spinning a bit and im having a really hard time finding the right words when i talk, like they're on the tip of my tongue but i cant say them. i feel super confused too. do u think i'm just dehydrated or is it heat exhaustion?",
